<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="p.paris;;23r" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">PParis23</xref></head><div lang="grc" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="edition"><div n="r" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>παρὰ Ταυγῆστος καὶ Ταῦστος δ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ιδ</supplied>υμ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῶ</supplied>ν τῶν ἐν <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τῶι</supplied> ἐν Μέμφει 

    <lb n="2"/>μεγάλῳ Σαραπιείωι. <choice><corr>ἀδικούμεθα</corr><sic>αδεικουμεθα</sic></choice> ὑπὸ Νε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">φό</supplied>ρ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υ</unclear>τος 

    <lb n="3"/>τῆ<add place="supralinear">ς</add> <subst><add place="inline">μητρὸς</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">μετρος</del></subst> ἡμῶν. καταλιποῦσα τὸν πατ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">έρα</supplied> ἡμῶν 

    <lb n="4"/>καὶ συνοικήσασα Φιλίππωι Σωγένου <choice><corr>στρατιώτῃ</corr><sic>στρατι<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ωτ</supplied>ης</sic></choice> ἐκ τῆς 

    <lb n="5"/>σημείας τοῦ Π<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">υ</unclear><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ρῶτος, ὁ δὲ Φίλιππος, κατ᾽ ἀπιστί-

    <lb n="6"/><choice><corr>αν</corr><sic>απιστηιην</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἐπέταξεν</corr><sic>επεταξαν</sic></choice> αὐτῷ <choice><corr>ἀποκτεῖναι</corr><sic>αποκτιναι</sic></choice> τὸν πατέρα ἡμῶν 

    <lb n="7"/><gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>γυν<gap extent="2" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>τι καὶ <choice><corr>σπασάμενος</corr><sic>ασπασαμενος</sic></choice> τὴν μάχαιραν κατέ-

    <lb n="8"/>τρεχεν αὐτόν. ἡ δὲ <choice><corr>οἰκία</corr><sic>οικιας</sic></choice> τοῦ πατρὸς ἡμῶν ἐνγὺς 

    <lb n="9"/>τοῦ ποταμοῦ ἐστιν, ἀπεπήδησε εἰς τὸν ποταμὸν 

    <lb n="10"/>καὶ κατακολυμβήσας ἕως <subst><add place="inline">ἔλθῃ</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ηλθη</del></subst> εἰς νῆσον ἐν τῶι <add place="supralinear">π<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>τα</add>μῶι 

    <lb n="11"/>καὶ πλοῖον <subst><add place="inline">ἀναλαμβάνει</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ανα<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>αμβανει</del></subst>, <choice><corr>καθιστᾷ</corr><sic>καιθειστα</sic></choice> αὐτὸν 

    <lb n="12"/>εἰς Ἡρακλήους <choice><corr>πόλιν</corr><sic>πολειν</sic></choice> καὶ ἀποθνῄσκει ἐκεῖ ὑπὸ τῆς 

    <lb n="13"/>λύπης. οἱ <choice><corr>ἀδελφοὶ</corr><sic>δελφοι</sic></choice> αὐτοῦ πορεύονται ἐπ᾽ αὐτὸν 

    <lb n="14"/>καὶ ἄγουσιν καὶ εἰς τὴν <choice><corr>νεκρ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ί</supplied>αν</corr><sic>νεκραν</sic></choice> <choice><corr>καθιστῶσιν</corr><sic>καθειστωσιν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="15"/>αὐτόν, <choice><corr>ἔτι</corr><sic>ετει</sic></choice> καὶ νῦν ἄταφός <choice><corr>ἐστιν</corr><sic>εστειν</sic></choice>. τὴν δὲ οὐσίαν 

    <lb n="16"/>αὐτοῦ ἔιληφεν καὶ ἐνοίκιον λαμβάνει κατὰ μῆνα 

    <lb n="17"/><expan>χα<ex cert="high">λκοῦ</ex></expan> <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="1400">Αυ</num>. ἐκβάλλουσα ἡμᾶς <choice><corr>ἀνεχωρή<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">σα</supplied>μεν</corr><sic>ανεχορημεν</sic></choice> <add place="supralinear">ἄνω</add> εἰς 

    <lb n="18"/>τὸ <choice><corr>Σαραπιεῖον</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">σαραπιειην</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">σαραπιει<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>ν</del></subst></sic></choice> <choice><corr>πεινῶσαι</corr><sic>πινοντες</sic></choice> πρὸς <choice><corr>Πτολεμ<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">αῖ</del>ν</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">πτολεμν</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">πτολεμ<del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">αι</del>ν</del></subst></sic></choice> <choice><corr>τῶ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ν</supplied></corr><sic>τω</sic></choice> ἐν κατο-

    <lb n="19"/>χῇ, ὁ δὲ <subst><add place="inline">Πτολεμαῖς</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable"><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/>τολεμαις</del></subst> φίλος ἡμῶν ἦν τοῦ πατρὸς, 

    <lb n="20"/>ἀναλαμβάνει ἡμ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ᾶ</supplied>ς καὶ τρέφει. γενομένου δὲ τοῦ πένθου<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς</supplied> 

    <lb n="21"/>κατάγουσιν ἡμᾶς πενθεῖν τῶι θεῶι. οἱ δὲ γνώριμοι 

    <lb n="22"/>αὐτῆς ἀναπίθουσιν ἡμᾶς δέξασθαι <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τὸν υ</supplied>ἱὸν αὐτῆς 

    <lb n="23"/>Παγχράτην, <choice><corr>ἵνα</corr><sic>εινα</sic></choice> <choice><corr>διακονῆι</corr><sic>δειακονει</sic></choice> ἡμῖν. <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">διασ</supplied>τέλλομεν 

    <lb n="24"/>αὐτὸν τοῦ <sic><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan></sic> <num value="17">ιζ</num> ἔτους  κομίσα<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σθαι ὧ</supplied>δε τὸ γινόμε-

    <lb n="25"/>νον ἡμῖν ἐκ βασιλικοῦ. 

    <lb n="26"/>καὶ <choice><corr>πάλιν</corr><sic>παλειν</sic></choice> <del rend="erasure" status="unremarkable">τοῦτον</del> οὗτος <choice><corr>κλέψας</corr><sic>κλεψασα</sic></choice> ἃ εἴχαμεν 

    <lb n="27"/>ἐν <add place="supralinear">τῷ</add> <choice><corr>Σαραπιείωι</corr><sic>σαραπειειωι</sic></choice> καὶ ἃ <choice><corr>ἐκομίσατο</corr><sic><subst><add place="inline">κομισατο</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">κομισας</del></subst></sic></choice> ἐκ βασιλικοῦ <subst><add place="inline">παρ᾽</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">περι</del></subst> ὑμῶν 

    <lb n="28"/><subst><add place="inline">ἐλαίου</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">ελθαιου</del></subst> <expan>με<ex cert="high">τρητὴν</ex></expan> <num value="1">α</num> καὶ <subst><add place="inline">ἀπῆλθεν</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">απελθεν</del></subst> πρὸ<add place="supralinear">ς</add> τὴν <subst><add place="inline">μητέρα</add><del rend="corrected" status="unremarkable">μητηρα</del></subst> αὐτοῦ. 

    <lb n="29"/>ὁ δὲ Πτολεμαῖς ὁ ἐν κατοχῇ ἐν τῷ αὐτῷ ἱερῶι 

    <lb n="30"/>τοῦ θεοῦ <choice><corr>ἐπιτάξαντος</corr><sic>επειταξαντος</sic></choice> ἀναλαμβάνει ἡμᾶς 

    <lb n="31"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="line"/> 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>παρὰ Πτολεμαίου Γλαυκίου <choice><corr>Μακεδόνος</corr><sic>μακ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ε</supplied>δ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ων</supplied></sic></choice> 

    <lb n="2"/><choice><corr>τοῦ</corr><sic>ο</sic></choice> ἐν κατοχῇ <choice><corr>ἔτος</corr><sic>ητη</sic></choice> ἤδη ἑνδέκατον </ab></div></div><div n="meta.3409a" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.3409a" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-0163-10-08" notBefore="-0163-04-01" type="textDate">1. Apr. - 8. Okt. 163 v.Chr. (Tage unsicher)</date></p></div><div n="meta.3409a" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Rückseite: UPZ I  82. Zur Datierung vgl. Skeat, Reigns, S. 14 und 33 - 34; Einleitung S. 188.</p></div><div n="meta.3409a" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="mentionedDates" type="commentary"><head>Erwähnte Daten</head><p>Z. 24: <date notAfter="-0164" notBefore="-0165" type="mentioned">165 - 164 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.3409a" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">UPZ</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">18</biblScope><biblScope type="side">R</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">3409</biblScope><biblScope type="parts">a</biblScope></bibl><bibl default="NO" type="DDbDP"><series>0245</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">18</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0245;1;18" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.3409a" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><listBibl default="NO"><bibl default="NO" type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">500